---
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="Career" description="Chirag Singhal — career timeline">
  <div style="padding-top: 2rem; max-width: 600px;">
    <h1 class="page-title">Career</h1>
    <p class="page-sub">Full-time roles and internships.</p>

    <div class="timeline">

      <!-- TCS -->
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--t-muted);margin-bottom:4px;">Jun 2025 – Present</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:14px;color:#fff;">Tata Consultancy Services</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--t-secondary);margin-bottom:8px;">Software Engineer</div>
        <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;">
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--t-secondary);padding-left:12px;position:relative;"><span style="position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--t-muted);">–</span>Optimized Python pricing engines — 60% latency reduction</li>
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--t-secondary);padding-left:12px;position:relative;"><span style="position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--t-muted);">–</span>Architected modular data validation pipelines via RESTful APIs</li>
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--t-secondary);padding-left:12px;position:relative;"><span style="position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--t-muted);">–</span>Automated CI/CD workflows, reduced production bugs</li>
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--t-secondary);padding-left:12px;position:relative;"><span style="position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--t-muted);">–</span>Built React.js UI for real-time backend configuration visibility</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- QRsay -->
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--t-muted);margin-bottom:4px;">Jul 2023 – May 2025</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:14px;color:#fff;">QRsay.com</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--t-secondary);margin-bottom:8px;">Software Developer — Full Stack</div>
        <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;">
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--t-secondary);padding-left:12px;position:relative;"><span style="position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--t-muted);">–</span>Full SDLC ownership of Food E-commerce platform (Python, Node.js, MongoDB)</li>
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--t-secondary);padding-left:12px;position:relative;"><span style="position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--t-muted);">–</span>40% reduction in API response times via DB tuning and indexing</li>
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--t-secondary);padding-left:12px;position:relative;"><span style="position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--t-muted);">–</span>Real-time order processing with Kafka event-driven architecture</li>
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--t-secondary);padding-left:12px;position:relative;"><span style="position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--t-muted);">–</span>Integrated secure payment gateways end-to-end</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
